        <li>Protect our rights, privacy, safety, or property</li>
        <li>Enforce our terms of service</li>
        <li>Investigate potential violations</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Business Transfers</h3>
      <p>
        In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets, your information may be transferred as part of that transaction, subject to equivalent privacy protections.
      </p>

      <h2 id="data-security">5. Data Security</h2>
      <p>We implement comprehensive security measures to protect your data:</p>

      <h3>Technical Safeguards</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Encryption:</strong> End-to-end encryption for sensitive data transmission and storage</li>
        <li><strong>Access Controls:</strong> Strict access controls and authentication systems</li>
        <li><strong>Network Security:</strong> Firewalls, intrusion detection, and secure network protocols</li>
        <li><strong>Regular Audits:</strong> Security assessments and vulnerability testing</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Data Protection Practices</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Data Minimization:</strong> We collect only necessary information</li>
        <li><strong>Retention Limits:</strong> Data is kept only as long as needed</li>
        <li><strong>Anonymization:</strong> Personal identifiers are removed for research and analytics</li>
        <li><strong>Secure Deletion:</strong> Proper disposal of data when no longer needed</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="ai-specific-privacy">6. AI-Specific Privacy Practices</h2>
      <p>Given our focus on AI technology, we implement special privacy considerations:</p>

      <h3>AI Training and Model Development</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>We use aggregated, anonymized data to improve AI models</li>
        <li>Personal conversations are not used to train public AI models</li>
        <li>You can opt out of AI improvement programs</li>
        <li>Sensitive content is filtered and protected during processing</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Memory and Context Systems</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>AI agents maintain conversation context to provide better experiences</li>
        <li>Memory data is encrypted and stored securely</li>
        <li>You can view, edit, or delete AI memory data at any time</li>
        <li>Memory systems respect your privacy preferences</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Voice and Audio Processing</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Voice data is processed securely and not stored permanently unless requested</li>
        <li>Audio processing occurs with explicit consent</li>
        <li>Voice prints and audio patterns are not used for identification</li>
        <li>You can disable voice features at any time</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="your-rights">7. Your Privacy Rights</h2>
      <p>You have comprehensive rights regarding your personal data:</p>

      <h3>Access and Control</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Data Access:</strong> Request copies of your personal data</li>
        <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Update or correct inaccurate information</li>
        <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion of your personal data</li>
        <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Export your data in a machine-readable format</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Privacy Controls</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Opt-out:</strong> Withdraw consent for data processing</li>
        <li><strong>Restrict Processing:</strong> Limit how we use your data</li>
        <li><strong>Object:</strong> Object to specific data processing activities</li>
        <li><strong>Automated Decision-Making:</strong> Opt out of automated profiling</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>How to Exercise Your Rights</h3>
      <p>
        To exercise any of these rights, you can:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Use the privacy controls in your account settings</li>
        <li>Contact our privacy team at <strong>privacy@aidigitalfriend.com</strong></li>
        <li>Submit a request through our privacy portal</li>
        <li>Contact our Data Protection Officer</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="international-transfers">8. International Data Transfers</h2>
      <p>
        As a global platform operated across the UAE, UK, and USA, your data may be transferred internationally. We ensure adequate protection through:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Standard Contractual Clauses (SCCs) approved by regulatory authorities</li>
        <li>Adequacy decisions by relevant data protection authorities</li>
        <li>Binding Corporate Rules for internal transfers</li>
        <li>Explicit consent where required</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="children-privacy">9. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        Our services are designed for users 13 years and older. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we become aware that we have collected information from a child under 13, we will delete it promptly.
      </p>
      <p>
        For the <strong>Red Teaming Academy</strong> (ethical hacking education), additional protections apply:
      </p>
      <ul>
